    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/646010/extras/b6c5daf3f99e44c2049d1124460f8f2f.poster.avif?t=1538513716\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/646010/extras/b6c5daf3f99e44c2049d1124460f8f2f.webm?t=1538513716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/646010/extras/b6c5daf3f99e44c2049d1124460f8f2f.mp4?t=1538513716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>没有人知道是谁建造了海岸边的古塔。小女孩认为，曾经肯定有水从巨大的水槽中流进村庄，但即便是她的祖父也不记得看到过水车的旧水轮转动过。如今，她和村里的其他孩子却需要往返于古塔和村庄之间，收集塔下的洞穴中冒出的一点点水。但当她唤醒埋藏在水坑下面的神秘光球后，一切都将改变。长久以来隐藏在洞穴墙壁上的图像散发出光芒，暗示着她那饱受干旱折磨的村庄有了新的希望，封闭了几个世纪的古塔大门，也第一次微微开启。伴着强烈的好奇心，小女孩勇敢地进入这台古老机器的废墟，去探索它那隐藏已久的秘密是否是开启她未来之路的钥匙。</i><br><br>一个小女孩和一个变形石人的温馨探险旅程，他们必须穿过古塔废墟，解决各种富有挑战性的难题，并重新启动休眠已久的机器。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/646010/extras/04e5d4db533a0d4929f8672e7eb5ba7c.poster.avif?t=1538513716\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/646010/extras/04e5d4db533a0d4929f8672e7eb5ba7c.webm?t=1538513716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/646010/extras/04e5d4db533a0d4929f8672e7eb5ba7c.mp4?t=1538513716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>探索10个内容丰富的游戏级别，从深入塔下的洞穴，到高耸在沙漠中饱受风吹日晒的塔顶。<br></li><li>利用女孩和石人的不同技能，解决古塔中的各种难题，穿过破碎的废墟，并重新启动休眠已久的机器。<br></li><li>帮助石人完成五种独特形式的进化，每次进化都会为这两位同伴带来新的能力，以帮助她们前进。<br></li><li>解读古塔中的神秘象形文字，寻找有关远古建造者和神秘石人起源的线索。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/646010/extras/0e1c8e86e36ae3f094590888576f8286.poster.avif?t=1538513716\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/646010/extras/0e1c8e86e36ae3f094590888576f8286.webm?t=1538513716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/646010/extras/0e1c8e86e36ae3f094590888576f8286.mp4?t=1538513716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
